@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((tmp * wp.sin(v0 + 0.53)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.59)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.88))
    tmp = wp.sin((0.38 + (v2 + 0.06 - v2 + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.23 + v2 + 0.97)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.89)) + v0)
    v0 = (v2 - ((v1 + 0.87 * v0 + 0.09) / 0.89))
    data[tid] = v0
